reviewText: Fantastic DVD on Palau, below water and above.  Beautiful photography.  Awesome keepsake of a trip to Palau diving without having to lug all the camera equipment!  I highly recommend this DVD!

IT IS A DELIGHT TO SEE THIS HEALTH VIGOROUS REEF AND ITS INHABITANTS IN THIS FILM.  SADLY, i MADE THIS DIVE JUST 6 SHORT YEARS AFTER THIS FILM (JUNE 2015), AND AM SHOCKED BY THE CHANGE (DETERIORATION) IN THE HEALTH OF THE REEF.  I IMAGINE ALL THE DIVERS HOOKING TO THE REEF AT BLUE CORNER HAS ALOT TO DO WITH THE FACT THAT THE CORALS AND REEF FISH ARE MOSTLY NON EXISTENT NOW.
Wow! Dazzling images, and a great message!
